## PWA Features

### Service Worker

The service worker provides:
- Static asset caching
- API response caching
- Offline fallback

### Push Notifications

Enable push notifications by setting `VITE_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY` in your environment.

### Install Prompt

The app shows an install prompt when the browser supports PWA installation.

## Environment Variables

| Variable | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `VITE_API_URL` | Backend API URL |
| `VITE_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY` | VAPID public key for push |
| `VITE_APP_VERSION` | App version |
| `VITE_APP_BUILD` | Build number |

